g.ns1:text:
\centering\noindent
$$
 \mtx{T}^*(b) = \argmin_{\mtx{T} \in [0,1]^{\cns{P}\times\cns{P}}} \sum_{p\in 1:\cns{P}}\sum_{q\in 1:\cns{P}} T^{p,q} C^{p,q}(b)
~~\textrm{subject to }
 \sum_{q\in 1:\cns{P}} \mkern-3mu T^{p,q} = 1,\,\mkern-4mu
 \sum_{q\in 1:\cns{P}} \mkern-3mu T^{q,p} = \cns{P}v^p(b) 
 ~~\forall p \in \range{\cns{P}}
$$

text.tspan: Optimal transport map per PoU basis
